data.title: ES2018 First Look - it changes everything
data.description:
ES2018 a.k.a. "ESSuper-Next" is out and it is awesome.
It has powerful new features like 
always-global-variables, 
common-keyword shortcuts, 
dot-syntax,
flow/typescript support

It's sure to be a game-changer.

Oh...and by the way, this is an April Fools video :)

data.description:

The 4 Ultimate has an anodized aluminum top and Cherry MX keyswitches, which, when combined, makes for an incredible typing experience.  The Das Keyboard Ultimate also features blank keycaps to promote more efficient typing (that's right, MORE efficient...because it breaks terrible habits)
